{"tid":826090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天璽加價最多五成仍獲承接 兩房5100萬","createTime":"2018-09-18T04:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T04:09:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e8dc3334ccc0a65eef744294bf97d6ce60dd4a5c","tid":826090,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00003/0c1862b3f0fe261fde986959eaf3b5fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00003%2F0c1862b3f0fe261fde986959eaf3b5fc.jpg&h=04c45c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超強颱風山竹橫掃香港後，令多區市面大受破壞，惟「周周有盤推」的新地(0016)，今日如期推售九龍站天璽5伙一手餘貨，提價幅度雖高達45%至50%，但今日依然售出3伙，其中一組客人連環購入天鑽璽77樓A、B室兩伙，單位實用面積分別1481及693方呎，相關單位均提價45%(相對2015年3月)，成交價分別1.089億元及5100萬元、呎價皆約7.35萬元，後者料再創全港兩房戶新高價。<br />\n<br />\n至於是次加幅最進取達50%的皇鑽璽78樓、實用1608方呎C室亦告售出，成交價更高逾1.233億元、呎價7.67萬元。<br />\n<br />\n另新地同系南昌站匯璽II，因超強颱風山竹襲港而順延至今日發售的33伙，則接近清袋。"},{"pid":"5dd514fb407fbeadee824c8419697ac28435d5c0","tid":826090,"uid":73,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"食正個風窗都唔爆隻<br />\n最少加100%啦"},{"pid":"b3ade353de09de8217e2d6fd9a6892c2c3583aaf","tid":826090,"uid":3177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:09:01.000Z","msg":"左手----右手"},{"pid":"28ccaa53a030959abd446680b4d42cebe24506c3","tid":826090,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:09:42.000Z","msg":"樓市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}